00:14:37.030 --> 00:14:39.270
How about this one?

00:14:39.270 --> 00:14:40.090
Same problem.

00:14:40.090 --> 00:14:42.660
It's alternating with
the same problem.

00:14:42.660 --> 00:14:43.650
Right?

00:14:43.650 --> 00:14:46.050
So the only response-- so
