00:39:42.780 --> 00:39:45.840
there was a pair of rabbits
at the beginning that

00:39:45.840 --> 00:39:51.570
didn't obey the rules for that
were true for the rest of time.

00:39:51.570 --> 00:39:54.210
That was x.

00:39:54.210 --> 00:39:58.720
And y of n, also you have to
add in the two previous values.

00:39:58.720 --> 00:40:03.490
That's kind of a rule
