00:40:26.840 --> 00:40:28.970
And they're indeed funny.

00:40:28.970 --> 00:40:31.490
You get the golden ratio
and you get the reciprocal

00:40:31.490 --> 00:40:33.500
of the golden ratio,
the negative reciprocal

00:40:33.500 --> 00:40:35.670
of the golden ratio.

00:40:35.670 --> 00:40:37.520
So that's really bizarre
because we end up

00:40:37.520 --> 00:40:40.622
